1
00:00:00,416 --> 00:00:05,083
Interviewer: When you entered
the church that served as a prison

2
00:00:06,083 --> 00:00:10,458
How did they treat you and
what was their approach?

3
00:00:10,458 --> 00:00:13,708
Did they take you
directly to the prison hall?

4
00:00:13,958 --> 00:00:17,458
Or was there an interrogation,
recording of information and details?

5
00:00:17,458 --> 00:00:19,166
How did they handle
your personal belongings?

6
00:00:19,583 --> 00:00:24,000
And what kind of
questions did they ask you?

7
00:00:24,958 --> 00:00:26,083
When we first entered

8
00:00:26,750 --> 00:00:28,583
The person told the other
that this one neglected prayer

9
00:00:28,583 --> 00:00:30,041
And that one was brought from
a wedding and was clean-shaven

10
00:00:31,083 --> 00:00:33,958
When he heard that one of us neglected prayer and
the other was clean-shaven, he lost his temper

11
00:00:33,958 --> 00:00:35,625
As if I had committed
something terrible

12
00:00:36,125 --> 00:00:38,083
I swore to him that I
was not neglecting prayer

13
00:00:39,333 --> 00:00:41,333
He said, Yes you are. Get inside

14
00:00:41,875 --> 00:00:43,583
They recorded our information
and took our belongings

15
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:45,458
And during the search,
they found cigarettes on me

16
00:00:46,625 --> 00:00:49,083
Interviewer: Where were the cigarettes?
Witness: I was keeping them here

17
00:00:50,125 --> 00:00:51,583
I was wearing pants at the time

18
00:00:53,375 --> 00:00:56,250
I was keeping cigarettes here, one
pack for me and one for my brother

19
00:00:57,083 --> 00:00:59,500
Interviewer: After they found
cigarettes on you, how did they treat you?

20
00:01:00,750 --> 00:01:03,083
They shouted and pushed me

21
00:01:03,458 --> 00:01:04,875
And asked me where I got them

22
00:01:04,875 --> 00:01:08,375
I told them they were mine, from a
while ago when I was working in the market

23
00:01:08,458 --> 00:01:10,875
I had stocked up, and
this was what remained

24
00:01:13,958 --> 00:01:16,583
Interviewer: And what happened
after that, after you went in?

25
00:01:16,583 --> 00:01:18,375
They recorded
information like full name

26
00:01:18,375 --> 00:01:20,333
Mother's name, and
place of residence

27
00:01:22,333 --> 00:01:24,458
He took me inside. I told him I was not
neglecting prayer and that I had a permit

28
00:01:24,458 --> 00:01:25,958
He said, No, you
are neglecting prayer

29
00:01:25,958 --> 00:01:28,000
He pushed me and
shoved me into the hall

30
00:01:28,083 --> 00:01:30,333
Interviewer: Alright, the person
who recorded your information

31
00:01:30,375 --> 00:01:35,166
Do you think this man
knew you from before?

32
00:01:35,833 --> 00:01:38,083
Interviewer: Or you did not know
him? Witness: No, I did not know him

33
00:01:38,458 --> 00:01:40,458
Interviewer: How old was he
approximately? What did he look like?

34
00:01:40,625 --> 00:01:43,583
He was about 30 or 28 years old

35
00:01:43,625 --> 00:01:45,333
Dark-skinned with a black beard

36
00:01:45,875 --> 00:01:48,458
Wearing the Qandahari
outfit and the Hisba robe

37
00:01:49,875 --> 00:01:53,375
Interviewer: Was this person
specifically assigned to this task?

38
00:01:53,458 --> 00:01:56,500
Or could any one of
them take the information?

39
00:01:57,333 --> 00:01:59,083
There was a person
sitting at the table

40
00:02:00,041 --> 00:02:03,166
He recorded the information,
then took the notebook and left

41
00:02:03,625 --> 00:02:05,083
He went to that church

42
00:02:05,166 --> 00:02:07,750
To the main computer to enter
the information, I do not know

43
00:02:09,208 --> 00:02:12,000
Interviewer: Then where did they send
you? Witness: They sent us to the hall

44
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:15,875
We stayed in the hall, and
when afternoon prayer time came

45
00:02:17,041 --> 00:02:18,875
They brought us in here

46
00:02:19,083 --> 00:02:20,250
I performed ablution here

47
00:02:21,125 --> 00:02:24,708
We prayed the afternoon prayer,
then about an hour after prayer

48
00:02:24,750 --> 00:02:28,750
They brought us all out
and divided us into groups

49
00:02:28,833 --> 00:02:30,583
They took us
upstairs to that room
